Just a note to KitKat and co: The Cybertronian Fire has scanner jams, at 
best, you'd be able to scan the outside. To get the 'plans of the ship', 
you'd either have to do what BrightBlade is doing, or what Feline and 
Skulletron are going to do. Phobia might have some of the ship scanned from 
his visit, but the jammers would most-likely have prevented him from getting 
more than half.

::Striker::

Striker raises an eyebrow. Spears seemed to be holding in alot of anger. He 
smiles. "We'll have enough time to get to the CF," he says, forgetting about 
Spears' fear of heights, "I could fly us there."

He blinks, realizing what he'd just said, "Or we could walk," he quickly adds 
on, hoping the first comment wouldn't drive Spears to panic.
